==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Nagyagite
<hw>Nag"yag*ite</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[So called from
<etsep>Nagyag</etsep>, in Transylvania.]</ety> <fld>(Min.)</fld> <def>A
mineral of blackish lead-gray color and metallic luster, generally of a
foliated massive structure; foliated tellurium. It is a telluride of
lead and gold.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Naiad</ent>⟦br⟧
